Took my little brother, @shane_puccio ,to Emerald Lake yesterday and decided to play around a little and did  some reverse climbing. 
.
Started at the end of “The Kind Traverse” and finished up “The Kind”.
Thought it felt like V11ish. To me, felt harder than The Kind Traverse. 
Anyone know if this has been done before??? 
Fun movement and a better finish!!! 👍😃
.
@scarpana @organicclimbing @frictionlabs @beam @kayaclimbing

Here’s a little uncut video of “Daytripper, V13/ 8B” I sent a few months back when all these sad and crazy fires in Colorado weren’t around! 
.
I hope everyone got out of Estes Park safely the other day and I hope all your homes will be ok! RMNP is one of my most favorite places to climb and it holds a very special place in my heart! 🙏 for Colorado and that these cooler temps with rain will help a lot!!! ❤️
.
@scarpana @evn_cbd

Took my little brother, @shane_puccio ,to Emerald Lake yesterday and decided to play around a little and did  some reverse climbing. 
.
Started at the end of “The Kind Traverse” and finished up “The Kind”.
Thought it felt like V11ish. To me, felt harder than The Kind Traverse. 
Anyone know if this has been done before??? 
Fun movement and a better finish!!! 👍😃
.
@scarpana @organicclimbing @frictionlabs @beam @kayaclimbing

I’m REALLY excited to announce my partnership with @beam !!! 😃😁
.
Climbing is a very demanding sport on your body. Through the many years of my climbing I have learned to realize that it is super important how I treat my body and therefore what I put in it. What you put in is what you get out!!! 
@beam makes high quality amazing products for different times of your workout and recovery aid.
A few of my favorites are,
The Dream Powder for a great nights sleep! Sleeping is such an important part of recovery! 
Another product is the Elevate powders. You can also get a variety pack so you can have all of them! :) 
.
Use code “ALEXPUCCIO” for a one time 15% off OR if you opt in for subscription you will get an even bigger discount!
